item.description:
@Java-RSPS-Noob wrote:

Bump

Server recently came back online. I have started to play this again and it’s quite fun now that the economy is quite fresh. The owner(s) have took some sound advice and are trying to keep the economy going in a straight path where the legends/hard difficulty players have to help supply the skilling resources such as food etc. They are doing an excellent job thus far.

There are still several bugs but they are all being worked out. Worthy of this grave dig.

To the mods: as far as I know RuneSens is the real owner of this server and so i would say this one validates the rule to stay open/is allowed to be bumped. Please let me know if I am in the wrong in bumping this.

Player base is needed to get this jump started!
